

OS Design
---------

Need:
  - Process library
      - Create process
      - Kill process
      - Save process state
      - Restore process state
      - Run queue
      - Sleep queue
  - Memory allocation (management)
      - Allocate n bytes
      - Free those bytes
  - Trap module to receive requests from applications
      - File system requests
      - Process requests (fork, exec, exit, kill, etc.)
      - Memory requests
  - File system
      - Open,close,write,read file
      - File system on disk
          - Superblock
	  - Directory of inodes
	  - Inode list of blocks
  - Device drivers
      - LCD display
      - Keyboard
      - Serial
      - IDE
      - NSTC display
      - Light pen
      - Clock interrupt
